Steps.Title: Welcome to Elobuddy!
Steps.Description:
Elobuddy is a powerful scripting tool for League of Legends.
With the help of the wizard you will explore the most common features Elobuddy is offering.

Steps.Title: Hacks - Tower Range Indicator
Steps.Description: Display tower range. Very helpful tool for laning and zoning enemies under tower.

Steps.Title: Hacks - Ping
Steps.Description: Display ping for all players during loading screen. Cannot be disabled.

Steps.Title: Suggested Addons - MasterMind
Steps.Description:
MasterMind adds several nice features to your game.
The aim of this addon is to be as accurate and beautiful as possible, while focusing on optimization.

Steps.Title: Suggested Addons - EvadeIC
Steps.Description: EvadeIC is a top tier evading addon, with smooth and human-like dodging.

Steps.Title: Suggested Addons - AramBuddy
Steps.Description: AramBuddy is an advanced AI addon which will help you with botting accounts in ARAM games.

Steps.Title: That's all for now!
Steps.Description:
You can get more addons and assistance from our official website https://www.elobuddy.net/
Have fun in the rift, summoner!
